## **CSS Requerido**

### **Estilos Oficiales en [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)**

```css
/* === LENIS SMOOTH SCROLL === */
html.lenis,
html.lenis body {
  height: auto;
}

.lenis.lenis-smooth {
  scroll-behavior: auto !important;
}

.lenis.lenis-smooth [data-lenis-prevent] {
  overscroll-behavior: contain;
}

.lenis.lenis-stopped {
  overflow: hidden;
}

.lenis.lenis-smooth iframe {
  pointer-events: none;
}
```

